    "Recently, the third technological revolution of Artificial Intelligence, following the development of the Internet and personal miniaturized computers, has brought about new developments, improvements, or features used for numerous purposes including reading, writing, artistic development as well as entertainment.",
    "A new era for teaching and learning in all fields of language instruction has begun with the appearance and widespread use of Artificial Intelligence technologies, best epitomized by the wellknown Chat-GPT text interaction tool.",
    "Previous research has shown that EFL learners often do not have sufficient latitude to output at a satisfactory level when writing in a second language.",
    "Technology and AI-enhanced tools open up a myriad of opportunities for language acquisition.",
    "Digitalization of the learning process extends beyond technical assistance and begins to mimic face-to-face language instruction."
